Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.11,0:02:42.78,op_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\3c&H8EC9DA&\c&HEAFCFD&}用冷酷的话刺伤你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.78,0:02:48.35,op_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\c&HFDFCDE&\2c&HBAB56A&\3c&HADB063&}就算全世界都不再信任你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.35,0:02:54.29,op_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\c&HFDFFD4&\3c&HC0B660&}给你扣上荆棘的王冠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.29,0:03:00.05,op_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\c&HF6F3D8&\3c&HAED256&}我依然只站在你身旁
