Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.03,0:22:02.23,song_CN_ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fade(200,200)\an2}今天却还是许下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.46,0:22:08.75,song_CN_ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fade(200,200)\an2}无法实现的愿望
